<h1>The Cost of Homelessness in Ireland</h1>
<div id="headline">
    <h3 class="highlight">
    <p>The <span class="em">cost</span> of homelessness in Ireland during <select name="year" id="year-select"
            onchange="yearSelected(this)">
            {{#each yearSelectData}}
                <option autocomplete="off" value="{{year}}" {{#if selected}} selected="{{selected}}" {{/if}} >{{year}} </option>
            {{/each}}
        </select> is/was <span class="em" id="data-cost">{{money currentSelect.total}}.</span></p>
        <p>That is enough money to build approximately {{houses currentSelect.total}} houses.</p>
    </h3>
</div>
<div id="midline">
    <h3 class="midlight">
    <p>That cost is composed of
        <span id="data-direct-cost">{{money currentSelect.direct.total}}</span> of <a href=""
            class="hoverTooltip">direct
            costs<span id="data-direct-cost-breakdown">{{money currentSelect.direct.HAP}} in Housing Assistance Payments,
                {{money currentSelect.direct.RAS}} in RAS spending,
                {{money currentSelect.direct.charities}} for the charitable sector.
            </span></a>, and</p>
        <span id="data-indirect-cost">{{money currentSelect.indirect.total}}</span> of
        <a href="" class="hoverTooltip">indirect
            costs<span id="data-indirect-cost-breakdown">{{money currentSelect.indirect.lost_tax_revenue}} in lost tax revenue from employment,
                {{money currentSelect.indirect.medical_spend}} in additional medical costs,
                {{money currentSelect.indirect.justice_spend}} in additional costs to the justice system.
            </span></a>.</p>
       </h3>
    </p>
</div>
{{#if links}}
    <div id="human-costs">
        <p>And incalculable human cost, as per the following stories:
            {{#each links}}
                <a href="{{link}}">{{title}}</a>
            {{/each}}
        </p>
    </div>
{{/if}}
